  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your mop and bucket and get ready to <strong>explore</strong> in the wild world of <i>War of the Wormholes</i>!<i> </i>Take the role of a janitor cleaning an Astronaut in the Box (a galactic arm spanning fast food chain).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.poster.avif?t=1744860246\" width=500 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.webm?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.mp4?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get recruited onto the <strong>Inconceivable</strong>, a formidable and feared privateer vessel of a desperate alliance of humans and aliens trying to fend off the darkest threats to the galaxy. Explore the ship and meet fantastical aliens and robots, find <strong>hidden rooms </strong>and<strong> secrets</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.poster.avif?t=1744860246\" width=500 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.webm?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.mp4?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a retro <i>point and click </i>adventure game set in a unique and immersive world filled with aliens, robots, adventure, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets galore!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saving and loading.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging Puzzles! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handcrafted pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No deaths and no dead ends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique world brought to life!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by Kevin Macleod and The Minute Hour.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive galactic guide. (In the main menu)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your mop and bucket and get ready to <strong>explore</strong> in the wild world of <i>War of the Wormholes</i>!<i> </i>Take the role of a janitor cleaning an Astronaut in the Box (a galactic arm spanning fast food chain).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.poster.avif?t=1744860246\" width=500 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.webm?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/71b360ca6bd1c7617dcf69d8789cab58.mp4?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get recruited onto the <strong>Inconceivable</strong>, a formidable and feared privateer vessel of a desperate alliance of humans and aliens trying to fend off the darkest threats to the galaxy. Explore the ship and meet fantastical aliens and robots, find <strong>hidden rooms </strong>and<strong> secrets</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.poster.avif?t=1744860246\" width=500 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.webm?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565940/extras/b34f79321f61282d7f7e54eec49cabb6.mp4?t=1744860246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a retro <i>point and click </i>adventure game set in a unique and immersive world filled with aliens, robots, adventure, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets galore!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saving and loading.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging Puzzles! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handcrafted pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No deaths and no dead ends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique world brought to life!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by Kevin Macleod and The Minute Hour.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive galactic guide. (In the main menu)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
